desmoj.extensions.applicationDomains.harbour

Class MyTruck

  • java.lang.Object
    • desmoj.core.simulator.NamedObject
      • desmoj.core.simulator.ModelComponent
        • desmoj.core.simulator.Condition<Truck>
          • desmoj.extensions.applicationDomains.harbour.MyTruck

  • public class MyTruck
extends Condition<Truck>
    This condition should check if the number of lane of the truck where he waits for an internal transporter at the HoldingArea is equal the number of the lane of this condition. The condition is used by an internal transporter to find the needed truck that it has to unload/load.
    See Also:
    Condition
